{"id":9563,"content":"<TABLE style=\"HEIGHT: 955px; WIDTH: 480px; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse\" cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 border=0>\r\n<TBODY>\r\n<TR>\r\n<TD class=3 vAlign=top width=90 align=center><BR><BR><BR><A href=\"#\" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"/yh/images/2014/07/1.jpg\" width=82 height=61></A><BR><BR><A href=\"#\" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"/yh/images/2014/07/2.jpg\" width=68 height=90></A><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><BR><A href=\"#\" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"/yh/images/2014/07/3.jpg\" width=81 height=55></A><BR><BR><BR><A href=\"#\" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"/yh/images/2014/07/4.jpg\" width=82 height=55></A><BR><BR><BR><BR><A href=\"#\" target=_blank><IMG border=0 alt=\"\" src=\"/yh/images/2014/07/5.jpg\" width=81 height=58></A><BR><BR><BR><BR></TD>\r\n<TD class=3 vAlign=top width=390 align=left>\r\n<P>【一家言】<BR><A href=\"/html/yjy/2014/77/BA63.html\" target=_blank>反思“国有经济强国论”</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．曹正汉<BR><A href=\"/html/yjy/2014/77/3845.html\" target=_blank>革新中国传统历史观</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．资中筠<BR><A href=\"/html/yjy/2014/77/1477164129E14D195439FBE1F9B3D5DB87.html\" target=_blank>对中国改革历史的思考</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．黄卧云</P>\r\n<P>【怀人篇】<BR><A href=\"/html/hyp/2014/77/EF47.html\" target=_blank>张钦礼一案的前前后后</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．陈　健<BR><A href=\"/html/hyp/2014/77/147716552779GEB95448DC6H21AKK1IC12.html\" target=_blank>真人马沛文</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．．郑本法</P>\r\n<P>【亲历记】<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2014/77/147717053IDJ6C954523K42GG00KBKDG2.html\" target=_blank>1960年的强拆</A>．．．．徐荫秀口述 高树林 李力跃记录整理<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2014/77/147717250H424G95467528E6238FE5009.html\" target=_blank>文革中的贵州省公安厅</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．．晏乐斌<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2014/77/147717100BKEA89547BJD5HBBHD3I0CKB.html\" target=_blank>关于红卫兵的一桩历史公案</A>．．．．．．．．．．．陈楚三<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2014/77/14771714510F31F95485KJ579938CB7DH2.html\" target=_blank>亳县“特殊案件”的记述</A>．．．．．．．．．．．．梁志远<BR><A href=\"/html/qlj/2014/77/1477171658H8K5B9549IGBJB9AFHIH2AI1.html\" target=_blank>红卫兵两次冲击人民日报</A>．．．．．．